{"tid":270803,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【六四廿八】逾百人遊行中聯辦   警扯黃旗斥勿煽動非法示威","createTime":"2017-06-04T14:26:02.000Z","updateTime":"2017-06-04T17:50:49.000Z","uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"24556cf4a9aa38bd4832c0a427aaa586ed18f511","tid":270803,"uid":48093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:26:02.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.nextmedia.com/images/e-paper/20170604/large/1496586109_0905.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.nextmedia.com%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170604%2Flarge%2F1496586109_0905.jpg&h=cd3b97cf&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n大專政關、社民連及人民力量等多個團體，呼籲港人參與六四集會後，遊行前往西區中聯辦，表明拒絕和解、繼續抗爭。他們並無向警方申請不反對通知書，遊行主辦單位人員在維園近銅鑼灣噴水池入口叫咪，警方即以大聲公警告，勿再煽動市民參與非法遊行。現場目測有100多人聚集等候出發。"},{"pid":"fc98908db5c366ec0ba4c8cb98ec8c8e5080326e","tid":270803,"uid":56428,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:29:45.000Z","msg":"11萬人得100人。 聽日返工呀"},{"pid":"9a5079c932ffd9d4bb9deb962c281de31ea71578","tid":270803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:47:12.000Z","msg":"做下SHOW<br />\n<br />\n都費撚事理佢地"},{"pid":"43ce54959222c86c5e0709a339340d3d598c3ab3","tid":270803,"uid":53687,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:48:54.000Z","msg":"班友肯好似黃之鋒喺926咁衝入去先算啦"},{"pid":"057b6c27aa770ebf66ca75ddef0baac4b708dde4","tid":270803,"uid":64966,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T14:51:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班友肯好似黃之鋒喺926咁衝入去先算啦</blockquote><br />\nAgger"},{"pid":"70f5a1d3a9b4d39fc76729ae9dea9062c397ec7e","tid":270803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T15:01:27.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>班友肯好似黃之鋒喺926咁衝入去先算啦</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n佢地只係想上下報紙之嘛<br />\n<br />\n記者影完相, 即時新聞出左<br />\n<br />\n佢地就散架啦<br />\n<br />\n佢地個建設民主支那行動係維持1小時架咋<br />\n<br />\n364日係冬眼狀態"},{"pid":"e5535b59d40c9512d6123194c0b0f1d69e9afe0c","tid":270803,"uid":92301,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:01:15.000Z","msg":"Lm"},{"pid":"c2aed18f42fd1fdc58efae767f2d2f2deaac81ab","tid":270803,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-06-04T17:50:49.000Z","msg":"多個團體在六四燭光集會後遊行至中聯辦 默哀後散去<br />\n[香港電台-港聞]<br />\n香港電台-港聞2017年6月5日 上午1:12<br />\n<br />\n多個團體約過百人，參加完維園六四燭光集會後，遊行至中聯辦，發表宣言並默哀，之後散去。<br />\n<br />\n遊行團體包括，社民連、人民力量及香港眾志等。沿途高叫「平反六四」、「釋放民運人士」等口號，警方一度宣布遊行未經批准，違反公安條例，並舉起黃旗。<br />\n<br />\n遊行人士抵達中聯辦後燃點燭光，發表宣言及默哀一分鐘。<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}